@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001/api/signup
@contentType = application/json

### 1. 建立報名 (第一次，應成功)
# @name createSignup
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "張同學",
  "email": "student@o365.tku.edu.tw",
  "phone": "0912888888"
}

### 2. 建立重複報名 (應失敗，回傳 409)
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "分身帳號",
  "email": "student@o365.tku.edu.tw",
  "phone": "0988777666"
}

### 3. 取得清單 (預設第一頁)
GET {{baseUrl}}

### 4. 取得清單 (分頁測試：第 1 頁，每頁 2 筆)
GET {{baseUrl}}?page=1&limit=2

### 5. 取得清單 (分頁測試：第 2 頁)
GET {{baseUrl}}?page=2&limit=2

### 變數設定 (從第 1 步的回應抓 ID)
@id = {{createSignup.response.body.id}}

### 6. 更新資料 (修改電話與狀態)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/{{id}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "phone": "0900000000",
  "status": "confirmed"
}

### 7. 刪除資料
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/{{id}}